Name: Rise of Zombies
About the game: Rise Of Zombies is a round based FPS zombie game, you participate in endless rounds of killing zombies and monsters and and rack up score to buy weapons that are scattered around the level. Currently it has one single player level(horror atmosphere) and 2 arcade mission and new content will be added monthly.
